de.mdelab.comparch

Interface ComponentType

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ArchitecturalElement, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ComponentTypeImpl

    public interface ComponentType
extends ArchitecturalElement
    A representation of the model object 'Component Type'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Name
    • Architecture
    • Required Interface Types
    • Provided Interface Types
    • Parameter Types
    • Instances
    • Reliability
    See Also:
    ComparchPackage.getComponentType()
